basic.production: Qinghai, Sichuan, Yunnan, Qing-Ba mountains in Shaanxi, Gansu
basic.blooming: Flowering period May-July, fruiting period August-October
basic.color: Flower color purple, red, orange, fruit color white

maintenance.sunlight: Should not be in direct contact with sunlight
maintenance.watering: Water slightly every day to keep soil moist
